'''Eric Santos''' (yavutse ku ya 31 Mutarama 1972), ni  umukinnyi wa filimi n'umwanditsi  wa Porutugali.   Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime ''Scoundrel'', ''The Compass'', ''Jikulumessu'' na ''Kaminey'' .  

== Umwuga ==
Santos yatangiye umwuga we mu 1996 akoresheje filimi ''Praça da Alegria'' . Kuva icyo gihe yagiye mu ikinamico, filime, urukurikirane, muri [[Angola]] no mu Giportigale. 

Niwe washinze kandi akaba n'umuyobozi mukuru wa 'Cast 39', Ikigo gishinzwe impano gikorera muri [[Porutugali]]. 

